1987;;Lionheart;;American;;Franklin J. Schaffner;;Eric Stoltz, Gabriel Byrne;;fantasy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lionheart_(1987_film);;Loosely based on the historical Children's Crusade, the story follows an exiled young knight, played by Eric Stoltz, who leads a band of orphans to join the Third Crusade with King Richard the Lionheart while protecting the children from the Black Prince (Gabriel Byrne), a disillusioned crusader turned child slave trader (not to be confused with the real-life Edward, the Black Prince).